phia Fusion|Stage 3 (5\u20135)|hide=y|\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=21|date= April 05 |year=2018|team1= Philadelphia Fusion |team1score=2 |team2score=3 |team2= Boston Uprising |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=22|date= April 07 |year=2018|team1= Florida Mayhem |team1score=1 |team2score=3 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=23|date= April 12 |year=2018|team1= Philadelphia Fusion |team1score=3 |team2score=2 |team2= Houston Outlaws |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=24|date= April 14 |year=2018|team1= London Spitfire |team1score=2 |team2score=3 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=25|date= April 19 |year=2018|team1= Philadelphia Fusion |team1score=2 |team2score=3 |team2= New York Excelsior |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=26|date= April 20 |year=2018|team1= Philadelphia Fusion |team1score=1 |team2score=3 |team2= San Francisco Shock |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=27|date= April 26 |year=2018|team1= Seoul Dynasty |team1score=3 |team2score=2 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=28|date= April 28 |year=2018|team1= Shanghai Dragons |team1score=2 |team2score=3 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=29|date= May 02 |year=2018|team1= Philadelphia Fusion |team1score=3 |team2score=1 |team2= Dallas Fuel |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=30|date= May 05 |year=2018|team1= Los Angeles Valiant |team1score=3 |team2score=2 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n}}\n\n{{OWL game log section|Philadelphia Fusion|Stage 4 (6\u20134)|hide=y|\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=31|date= May 17 |year=2018|team1= Boston Uprising |team1score=1 |team2score=3 |team2= Philadelphia Fusion |location= Burbank, CA}}\n{{Overwatch collapsible box|match=32